<h1>Progress Bar Worker</h1>

<p>In this example, clicking the <strong>Start Job</strong> button will launch a Sidekiq worker and begin polling the server every few seconds. </p>

<p>The worker loops for 10 iterations. Each time, it increases the worker progress by 10% then sleeps for one second.</p>

<p>The progress bar updates itself every time the page polls the server.</p>

<div hx-target="this" hx-swap="outerHTML">
  <h3>Start Worker</h3>
   <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" hx-post="/progress_bar_worker/start">Start Job</button>
</div>
